title: Kelenu Onye Tigbuworo Ndi Eze Di Uku (Abu oma 136, 17)
lyrics:
Dibia U - Ku 
 Dibia U - Ku 
 Jisus Kraist bu dibia uku

title: Kelenu Onye Tigbuworo Ndi Eze Di Uku (Abu oma 136, 17)
lyrics:
Tonu Chineke onye bu dike n’agha, 
 O - meriwo ndi iro Ya nagha. (DC) 
 E-E-E, Omeriwo, E.E. Omeriwo E.E. 
 Omeriwo ndi iro Ya nagha. (DC)

title: Ume we ba nimee ha, ha we di ndu. (Eze. 37, 3-100)
lyrics:
Bue amuma gwa umu madu - 
 Okpukpu gadi ndu ozo. (DC) 
 Chi-neke bu onye puru ime, 
 Ka ndi nwuru anwu site n’onwu bilie, 
 Okpukpu gadi ndu ozo

title: Menu Ihe nda, debekwa Ya. (Mt. 23:3)
lyrics:
Ma mme okwu Ya 
 Ma mme okwu Ya 
 Ma mme okwu Ya - Ozuwo 
 Ozuworomuo ---

title: Ngozi diri ndi agahu n’nche. (Abu 61:4)
lyrics:
Oburu na Jisus abia ikpe uwa ikpe. (DC) 
 O - gasom, “Ka mburu otu onye: 
 Onye ikpe na’gagh ama
